snippet.title: Catsperience - Trailer
snippet.description:
Catsperience on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/15...​
Discord: https://discord.gg/H5sPFX4egY​

Experience what it’s like to live like a real cat. Eat, sleep, be a jerk. Repeat. Oh wait, there is a problem. The food provider is missing, what will you do now? A blue-blooded cat doesn't hunt after all. Find him befur you will be in need of such a menial task.

Before you purchase please consider that this game was developed by a very passionate cat lovin' couple with the help of Cirmi the demonic tomcat who inspiered the story and not by a huge team. Honestly, we won't be surprised if Cirmi sees us as the protagonist of the game sees his owner.
